---
import "../styles/global.css";
---

<main>
  <section class="full">
    <header>
      <h3>Financial Projections</h3>
      <p class="fintext">
        Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit, sed do eiusmod
        tempor incididunt ut labore et dolore magna aliqua. Ut enim ad minim
        veniam, quis nostrud exercitation ullamco laboris nisi ut aliquip ex ea
        commodo consequat.
      </p>
    </header>
    <ul role="list">
      <li>
        <h3>The Balance Sheet</h3>
        <p class="litext">
          The Balance Sheet is a summary of the assets and liabilities and
          equity of a business at a specific point of time.
        </p>
      </li>

      <li>
        <h3>Income Statement</h3>
        <p class="litext">
          The Income (Profit and Loss) Statement, commonly referred to as the
          P&L statement, summarizes the revenue and expenses for a specific time
          period (one month, one quarter, one year, etc.)
        </p>
      </li>

      <li>
        <h3>Financial Plan</h3>
        <p class="litext">
          Keep your information current and review the documents on a regular
          basis (monthly or more often if needed). Review them with key
          individuals within your company.
        </p>
      </li>

      <li>
        <h3>Financial Ratios</h3>
        <p class="litext">
          Ratios are useful when comparing your company with the competition on
          financial performance and also when benchmarking the performance of
          your company.
        </p>
      </li>
    </ul>
  </section>
</main>
<style>
  section {
    background-color: var(--secondary-one);
    padding: 4rem;
  }

  header h3 {
    font-size: var(--heading-one);
    color: var(--primary-three);
    font-family: "Cabin", sans-serif;
    line-height: 3.625rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    font-style: normal;
  }

  .fintext {
    font-size: var(--p-size);
    font-weight: 400;
    font-family: "Lato", sans-serif;
    line-height: 1.475rem;
  }

  .litext {
    line-height: 1.475rem;
  }
  ul:has(> li:nth-child(2)) li:nth-child(2) {
    background: var(--primary-three);
    color: #fff;

    h3 {
      color: var(--secondary-two);
    }
  }
  :root {
    --content-width: 50rem;
  }

  main {
    padding-block: 4rem;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns:
      [full-start]
      1fr
      [content]
      minmax(0, var(--content-width))
      1fr
      [full-end];
    column-gap: 1rem;

    > * {
      grid-column: 2;
    }

    .full {
      grid-column: 1 / -1;
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: inherit;
      row-gap: 3rem;

      > * {
        grid-column: 2;
      }

      > ul {
        scroll-snap-type: x mandatory;
        grid-column: 1 / -1;
        padding-inline: max(1rem, 50% - var(--content-width) / 2);
        padding-block-end: 1rem;

        li {
          scroll-snap-align: center;
        }
      }
    }
  }

  ul {
    display: flex;
    gap: 2rem;
    overflow-x: auto;

    li {
      flex-basis: min(300px, 90%);
      flex-shrink: 0;
      background: #ebebeb;
      color: #595566;
      border-radius: 8px;
      font-size: 1rem;
      padding: 2.75rem 2.1875rem;
      align-self: start;

      h3 {
        font-weight: 700;
        font-size: 1.5625rem;
      }
    }
  }

  h2,
  h3 {
    all: revert;
    color: #181818;
    margin-block: 0 0.625rem;
    line-height: 1.125;
  }

  h2 {
    font-size: 2.8125rem;
  }

  header {
    color: #595566;

    p {
      max-inline-size: 67ch;
      line-height: 1.475rem;
    }
  }
</style>
